items.title: Trump admin live updates: Freedom Caucus chair says 'no way' budget bill passes today
items.description: Freedom Caucus Chairman Andy Harris said there is “no way” the “One Big Beautiful Bill Act” passes in the House on Wednesday.

items.title: Trump meets with GOP holdouts as negotiations over agenda bill falter
items.description: House Republicans have worked through the night to move a megabill advancing President Donald Trump's legislative agenda through a key committee.

items.title: What is SALT and why does it threaten Trump's 'Big Beautiful Bill?'
items.description: The future of President Donald Trump's "Big Beautiful" federal spending bill could come down to SALT tax deductions.

items.title: WATCH:  80-year-old Vietnam veteran graduates from university
items.description: An 80-year-old Vietnam veteran graduated from South Carolina State University to a roar of applause from his graduating class.

items.title: Dow closes down 800 points as bond sell-off rattles markets
items.description: The bond sell-off coincided with deficit concerns over a tax cut bill.
